'''Kraen Weest''' was a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Commander/Legends|commander]] in charge of the [[Decimator (war machine)|Decimator]] [[Decimator Facility|facilities]] of [[Eredenn Prime]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. He was [[Battle of Eredenn|killed]] by [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederate]] forces under the command of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Sev'rance Tann/Legends|Sev'rance Tann]].

